Author: SubBiscuit
Text: Propel makes zero cal electrolyte powder if that would help you reduce the harm to your body

Author: pabstpumpkinbeer
Text: Please try to eat something.   I find that the longer I restrict, the harder it is to eat again.   What would feel okay right now? I used to find soup easy to eat after not eating for awhile. Maybe some soup with a couple of crackers or another piece of toast? Or maybe some more Cheerios with some milk/yogurt and fruit?
